    3. Three FIND-006 inline parser stubs returning `body: "body"` → `body: makeBody("body")` (replace_all hit all 3).
- pipeline.test.ts: added `Body` to the imports and added the same `makeBody` helper.
  Replaced the single raw-string occurrence in the happy-path parser stub: `body: "Body text"`
  → `body: makeBody("Body text")`.
- step3-hydrate-feed.test.ts and step4-initialize-capture.test.ts: already used
